    EIROforum teachers school  

            Thu, 2011-04-21 10:57 — sis
      
   
     
	  
 
	Dear Science in School subscribers, 
 
	Many of you may be interested in the forthcoming teacher workshop given by EIROforum, the publisher of Science in School. The deadline for applications is fast approaching, so you will need to apply soon. 
 
	This free, three-day course is entitled ‘Physics and chemistry of life’ and is open to European science teachers. It will take place at the European Photon and Neutron Science Campus in Grenoble, France, from 9-12 October 2011.    

   
     
                 
         

              Read more  
 584 reads 
  
       

    
   
    

 


